'''Piklin Katt''' was the [[Baron Administrator/Legends|baron administrator]] of [[Tindark]] on [[Cularin/Legends|Cularin]]. He was [[Death/Legends|murdered]] in his [[Sleep/Legends|sleep]] in [[40 BBY/Legends|40 BBY]]. It was clearly an [[Assassin/Legends|assassination]], though no one knew who would want Katt dead.

